WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
&lt;h2&gt;Iran War — Evening Update&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Trump extended the Strait of Hormuz

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
deadline by 10 days — Iran now has until ~April

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
7 to reopen the strait. Dubai crude benchmark at $126/barrel,

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
up 76% since the war started. Pakistan now acting as

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
intermediary. Iranian Red Crescent: 1,900 killed since Feb 28. In

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Lebanon, 1,142 killed including 122 children.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;DHS Shutdown&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;TSA workers should start

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
seeing paychecks as early as Monday, March 30.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Financial&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bank of America

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.000
agreed to pay $72.5M to settle Epstein-related lawsuit. Anthropic approaching

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:36.000
$19B annualized revenue.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Apple&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Apple partnering with Google to use 1.2T parameter

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:39.200
Gemini model for reimagined Siri in iOS 26.4.&lt;/p&gt;
